\c 21
\s Ukubusa kukaManase
\p
\v 1 UManase wayeleminyaka elitshumi lambili lapho esiba yinkosi; wabusa iminyaka engamatshumi amahlanu lanhlanu eJerusalema. Lebizo likanina lalinguHefiziba\x + 2 Lan. 33.1-9.\x*.
\v 2 Wasesenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* njengokwamanyala ezizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* eyazixotsha elifeni phambi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli\x + 16.3.\x*.
\v 3 Ngoba wabuya wakha indawo eziphakemeyo uyise uHezekhiya ayezichithile\x + 18.4. 23.4,6.\x*, wamisela uBhali amalathi, wenza isixuku, njengokwenza kukaAhabi inkosi yakoIsrayeli\x + 21.13. 1 Kho. 16.32,33.\x*, wakhothamela ibutho lonke lamazulu, walikhonza\x + 17.16. 23.5. Dute. 4.19.\x*.
\v 4 Wasesakha amalathi endlini yeN\nd kosi\x + Jer. 7.30. 32.34. Hez. 7.20. 8.6.\x*\nd*, iN\nd kosi\nd* eyathi ngayo: EJerusalema ngizabeka ibizo lami\x + 21.7. 23.27. 2 Sam. 7.13. 1 Kho. 8.29. 9.3. Dute. 12.11. Hlab. 132.13,14.\x*.
\v 5 Wasesakhela ibutho lonke lamazulu amalathi\x + 17.16. 23.5. Dute. 4.19.\x* emagumeni womabili endlini yeN\nd kosi\x + 23.12. 1 Kho. 6.36. 7.12. 2 Lan. 4.9.\x*\nd*.
\v 6 Wasedabulisa indodana yakhe emlilweni\x + Levi 18.21.\x*, wachasisa ngemibono\x + Levi 19.26.\x*, wenza imilingo\x + 17.17. Gen. 44.5.\x*, wasebenza labalamadlozi labalumbayo\x + 23.24. Levi 19.31.\x*. Wenza okubi kakhulu emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* uku\add yi\add*thukuthelisa\x + 21.15. 22.17. 23.19. Dute. 4.25.\x*.
\v 7 Wasemisa isithombe esibaziweyo sesixuku ayesenzile endlini, iN\nd kosi\nd* eyakhuluma ngayo kuDavida lakuSolomoni indodana yakhe \add yathi\add*: Kulindlu, leJerusalema engiyikhethe kuzo zonke izizwe zakoIsrayeli, ngizabeka ibizo lami kuze kube nininini\x + 21.4. 23.4.\x*.
\v 8 Kangisayikuzulisa unyawo lukaIsrayeli luphume futhi elizweni engalinika oyise, kuphela uba bezananzelela ukwenza njengakho konke engabalaya khona langokomlayo wonke inceku yami uMozisi eyabalaya wona\x + 2 Sam. 7.10.\x*.
\v 9 Kodwa kabalalelanga; uManase wasebaphambukisa ukuthi benze okubi okwedlula izizwe iN\nd kosi\nd* eyazichitha phambi kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli.
\p
\v 10 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma ngezinceku zayo abaprofethi isithi:
\v 11 Ngenxa yokuthi uManase inkosi yakoJuda wenzile lamanyala\x + 21.2. 23.26. 24.3,4. Jer. 15.4.\x*, wenze okubi okwedlula konke amaAmori akwenzayo\x + 1 Kho. 21.26.\x*, ayephambi kwakhe, wonisa loJuda\x + 21.9,16. 1 Kho. 14.16.\x* ngezithombe zakhe\x + 21.21. 23.24. Dute. 29.17.\x*.
\v 12 Ngakho itsho njalo iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu kaIsrayeli: Khangela, ngiletha okubi phezu kweJerusalema loJuda kuthi laye wonke ozwayo indlebe zakhe zombili zizakhenceza \add ngakho\x + 1 Sam. 3.11.\x*\add*.
\v 13 Ngizakwelula phezu kweJerusalema intambo yeSamariya\x + Isa. 28.17. Isa. 34.11. Lilo 2.8. Amos 7.7,8.\x*, lentambo yokulinganisa yendlu kaAhabi, ngiyesule iJerusalema njengowesula umganu, awesule awumbokothe.
\v 14 Njalo ngizatshiya insali yelifa lami, ngibanikele esandleni sezitha zabo, babe ngokubanjiweyo lempango kwezitha zabo zonke,
\v 15 ngenxa yokuthi benzile okubi emehlweni ami, bayangithukuthelisa, kusukela osukwini oyise abaphuma ngalo eGibhithe ngitsho kuze kube lamuhla.
\v 16 Futhi-ke uManase uchithile igazi elinengi kakhulu elingelacala waze wayigcwalisa iJerusalema kusukela ekuqaleni kuze kube sekucineni, ngaphandle kwesono sakhe enza ngaso uJuda ukuthi one, ukwenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd*.
\p
\v 17 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaManase, lakho konke akwenzayo, lesono sakhe asonayo, kakubhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoJuda\x + 2 Lan. 33.11-19.\x*?
\v 18 UManase waselala laboyise, wangcwatshelwa esivandeni sendlu yakhe\x + 2 Lan. 33.20.\x*, esivandeni sikaUza\x + 21.26. 2 Sam. 6.6-8. 1 Lan. 13.7-11. 2 Lan. 26.23.\x*. UAmoni indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\s Ukubusa kukaAmoni
\p
\v 19 UAmoni wayeleminyaka engamatshumi amabili lambili lapho esiba yinkosi; wabusa iminyaka emibili eJerusalema\x + 2 Lan. 33.21-25.\x*. Lebizo likanina lalinguMeshulemethi indodakazi kaHaruzi weJotiba\x + Nani 33.33.\x*.
\v 20 Wasesenza okubi emehlweni eN\nd kosi\nd* njengokwenza kukaManase uyise\x + 21.2-6,11.\x*.
\v 21 Wahamba ngendlela yonke uyise ahamba ngayo, wakhonza izithombe uyise azikhonzayo, wakhothama kuzo.
\v 22 Wayidela iN\nd kosi\nd*, uNkulunkulu waboyise, kahambanga ngendlela yeN\nd kosi\x + 22.17. 1 Kho. 11.33.\x*\nd*.
\p
\v 23 Izinceku zikaAmoni zasezimenzela ugobe, zabulala inkosi endlini yayo.
\v 24 Kodwa abantu belizwe babatshaya bonke labo ababenzele inkosi uAmoni ugobe; abantu belizwe basebebeka uJosiya indodana yakhe ukuba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\p
\v 25 Ezinye-ke zezindaba zikaAmoni azenzayo kazibhalwanga yini egwalweni lwemilando yamakhosi akoJuda?
\v 26 Wasengcwatshelwa engcwabeni lakhe esivandeni sikaUza\x + 21.18.\x*. UJosiya indodana yakhe wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
